# Freshly-ingested demo cases (Console → "Initiate a new discovery" → upload your own documents)
# stage their files under inputs/<slug>/ and write results under out/<slug>/. These are transient
# run artefacts. The committed reference corpora (o2c, p2p) are already tracked, so git ignores
# never affect them — this only keeps NEW untracked ingest dirs out of the working tree.
inputs/*/
out/*/

# keep the committed reference domains addable
!inputs/o2c/
!inputs/p2p/
!out/o2c/
!out/p2p/
